same speed, speed v.

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:52.392
And we already have a
relationship that we've explored

00:02:52.392 --> 00:02:57.375
in previous videos between
speed and angular velocity.

00:02:57.375 --> 00:02:59.700
We have seen that the speed,

00:02:59.700 --> 00:03:02.142
I'll do it in a new color here.

00:03:02.142 --> 00:03:05.342
I'll say v for speed with
no arrow, not bolded,

00:03:05.342 --> 00:03:06.792
